{"tid":1773230,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英文新口號 Be aware or be next","createTime":"2019-12-07T10:07:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-07T12:02:29.000Z","uid":147785,"like":36,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"24d7ef19e4b93ee51478a50743259f90a400afe5","tid":1773230,"uid":147785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T10:07:27.000Z","msg":"相信大家都睇過Avi Yemini 呢個記者<br />\n係澳洲 曝露晒班小粉紅既恐怖<br />\n之前有條片<br />\n<br />\n小粉紅唔知示威定想阻住手足示威<br />\n小粉紅: 只有一個中國 不要港獨!<br />\nAvi: 但五大訴求 入面都冇要求港獨?<br />\n小粉紅: 只有一個中國 不要港獨!<br />\nAvi: 其實你知唔知五大訴求係邊五個?<br />\n小粉紅: (問隔離果個) 咩係五大訴求?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家佢黎咗香港幫手向澳洲宣傳啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QRUAjjTh_bU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DQRUAjjTh_bU&d=dMuVdPjJf30Qxtl2jkPsRAQPoALeJAOsJ3HVvkpnkS8%3D&h=bd75bff7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QRUAjjTh_bU</a><br />\n<br />\n咁啱聽到 6:26 個靚女 英文好得黎 仲有句好有力既對外口號<br />\n<br />\n「be Aware or be Next」<br />\n<br />\n5隻字 足夠話比世界各地既人知 香港既事唔係他國事務 中共既滲透係全面性的(all the ways)<br />\n<br />\n唔想自己國家日後變到香港咁 就唔該保持警覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af784c0fc4f9bf86b99a863e58972631e52e335c","tid":1773230,"uid":140538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T10:07:41.000Z","msg":"人血饅頭王HK Apocalypse 梁樂聞無去過示威!搵黃色經濟圈水原來真藍絲,俾咗資料小心!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1773154\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1773154</a>"},{"pid":"69d25f1a6710d9d7ad01a498f8a8836bd51a4a25","tid":1773230,"uid":147785,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T10:08:05.000Z","msg":"「be Aware or be Next」<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fff72ace8870589a1a1db59e0131370a35fb91b7","tid":1773230,"uid":253978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0